#1. Split training set and test set
ind <- sample(2, nrow(data), replace=TRUE, prob=c(0.7, 0.3))

trainData <- data[ind==1,]
testData <- data[ind==2,]
trainData

#2. Training set Decision Tree : ctree() "conditional inference tree", Decision Tree

bio_ctree <- ctree(class ~ b+c+d+f, data=trainData, ctree_control(split="gini"))
Error in ctree_control(split = "gini") : unused argument (split = "gini")
print(bio_ctree)
